      <section id="id7788271">
        <title>Om oppervlakte te bereken deur te ondersoek en te skat [LU 4.8.2]</title>
        <para id="id12336313"/>
        <list id="id5743777" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>Vir hierdie aktiwiteit moet julle in groepe van drie verdeel. Julle mag ‘n sakrekenaar gebruik om die probleme op te los. Werk mooi netjies en toon ‘n duidelike uiteensetting van die antwoorde. Lekker kopkrap!</item>
        </list>
        <para id="id13937316">1. ’n Boer moet ’n kamp vir kalwers met draad omhein.</para>
        <figure id="id6180572">
          <media id="id6180572_media" alt="">
            <image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/graphics1-7655.png" id="id6180572__onlineimage" height="166" width="367"/>
          </media>
        </figure>
        <para id="id13915723">1.1 Bereken hoeveel draad nodig is om die kamp te omhein.</para>
        <para id="id5767748">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id5840255">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id5761646">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id6495103">1.2 Indien die pale van die draad 1 meter uitmekaar geplant word, hoeveel pale is nodig?</para>
        <para id="id13416402">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id21734310">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id13668237">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id8056845">2. Die nuwe hokkieveld moet met grassaad gesaai word. Die afmetings van die veld is 112 m by 75 m. Indien die grassaad R1,20 per m<sup>2</sup> kos, wat beloop die koste van die hele projek?</para>
        <para id="id12851443">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id11782783">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id7000478">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id8984718">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id5759362">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id11956879">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id14449967">3. Indien ’n vierkantige speelterrein met ’n lengte van 45 m geteer word, is die totale koste R56 679,75. Wat is die koste van teer per 1 m<sup>2</sup>?</para>
        <para id="id5383290">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id6985357">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id13308391">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id13926056">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id6090492">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id17558682">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id7559106">4. ’n Gedeelte van die badkamermuur van 2,25 m by 0,75 m moet met nuwe teëls bedek word. Die teëls is vierkantig met ’n lengte van 15 cm. Hoeveel teëls is nodig?</para>
        <para id="id11869274">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id13430154">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id20606093">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id11818796">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id8242951">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id13213939">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
        <para id="id13947761">5. ’n Klaskamer het ’n oppervlakte van 50,32 m<sup>2</sup>. Indien die lengte 7,4 m is, wat is die breedte?</para>
